```mermaid
    classDiagram
        class User {
            +first_name: string
            +last_name: string
            +user_name: string
            +email: string
            +password: string
        }

        class Platform {
            +platform_name: string
            +platform_link: string
            +instance_url: string
            +token: string
            +api_login_username: string
            +api_login_password: string
        }

        class Account {
            +status: boolean
        }

        User "1" *-- "0..*" Account : has
        Platform "1" *-- "0..*" Account : is used by
```
